<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.3.7">
<l>āvari vaiceyta ṟivā rañcaṉa māmalai pōlē</l>
<l>mēvuci ṉattaṭal vēḻam vīḻamu ṉintaḻa kāya</l>
<l>kāvima larneṭuṅ kaṇṇār kaitoḻa vītiva ruvāṉ</l>
<l>tēvarva ṇaṅkutaṇ tillaic cittira kūṭattuḷ ḷāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Who is the one who is accustomed to doing these [deeds]?</l>
<l rend="indent">He who appeared on the street</l>
<l>Having raged so that the angry war elephant, which approached</l>
<l rend="indent">like a great kohl[-colored] mountain, fell,</l>
<l>As ladies with beautiful long eyes [like] blue-lily [petals]</l>
<l rend="indent">adored [him], palms [joined],</l>
<l>He is the one present in Citrakūṭam in cool Tillai</l>
<l rend="indent">where the gods worship.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
